Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 刘备派人送来一份拜帖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就知道他会给我来信 你猜猜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那信上头都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 我可猜不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连这都猜不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你今后如何做到料敌于先
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何才能做军中主将呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我替你猜一猜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.59,0:00:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备此信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开头嘛 肯定是奉承我一番
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他会替陶谦陪罪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为毕竟是他的部将杀了家父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后 他会劝我退军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄如晤 玄德百拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长安一会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下铭心刻骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄台之文韬武略如日照昆仑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄台之心胸大志如江海奔腾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下不胜仰慕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州刺史陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实乃宽厚仁德之君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其部下叛逆之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能尽归于其主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如今 兄之父已仙逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如逝水不可复归
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦愧恨无地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愿倾其财物 赔偿兄台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以稍赎其罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备斗胆进言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}盼兄台撤军言和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}化干戈为玉帛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倘能如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但徐州百姓感兄台大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:02:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下人也必称颂兄台之名义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则战端一开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玉石同焚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备不才
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愿与陶使君生死与共
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他刘备不过是一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}织席贩履的匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢来同我做对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传令下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}破城之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州城的男女老幼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全部斩尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以慰家父在天之灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们没有那么多的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}供养几十万战俘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 败报到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兖州出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是 昨天夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布率兵一举偷袭了兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}攻破了城 城中我军残部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正在浴血奋战中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布一介匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他哪里来的如此胆识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢偷袭我的兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 陈宫做了吕布的军师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来是陈公台在指使他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 兖州一旦失陷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我数万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可就无家可归了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全军即刻回师兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 那徐州怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等我战罢吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回来再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不妨做个顺水人情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卖刘备个面子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你替我复刘备一信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就说我接受他的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撤军言和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜谢刘公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不敢当 不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万万不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德一纸信文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}斥退了曹军五万铁骑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}使徐州免于战祸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}转危为安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事足以证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德忠肝义胆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}光照千秋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州五十万官民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}深感玄德君再造之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜谢玄德公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德老弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老夫年迈 犬子无才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州六郡只有在刘使君的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}治驭之下才可能太平昌盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经征求过徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所有文武官员的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们都愿意你提领徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请看在众人份上 担此任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶公 陶公深情厚意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备极为感化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但此尊关防
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备绝不敢受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此行是来救徐州而不是图徐州的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在 曹操大军已撤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待我饮罢此茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也该履行诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重归平原县了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请留步 刘公请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请留徐州城主持大业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各位快快请起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德老弟啊 看见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让你统领徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是百姓的真情实意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绝非你贪图徐州啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请看在众人的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}担此任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不成 陶公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这是逼我现在就离开徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请留步 请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请留步啊 请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使你不统领徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不能弃徐州而去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则 曹操定然复返
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州早晚要落到奸雄的囊中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样吧 我拨出一个边城小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可领军暂住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们可以形成一个特角之势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一旦有警
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们可以相互应援啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}至于你部所需粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全部由我供给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 谨遵陶公所命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好好 开宴 上酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请请请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘公 快请 快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:08:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊 祸事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶公 你的病不算是祸事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待来年开春定可康复
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你只需安心静养
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是说我的病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是说徐州要大难临头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚刚接报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操就半日 大败吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他可以腾出手来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马上再打徐州了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鸟之将死其鸣也哀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人之将死其言也善哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老夫我有几句话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我希望 在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你我之间不要再有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虚言客套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道 你们刘关张三兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}急需一方属地作为立身之本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你刘备不是不想得到徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恰恰相反 你想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你比任何人都想得到徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只不过呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你名节重于性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不想趁我之危罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶公明见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州只有托付于你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别无他人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我给朝廷的奏章
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经写在我的遗嘱里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我死后即发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夭下英雄众多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论如何也轮不到我刘备做徐州牧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那还有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍四世三公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}威名满天下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术胸怀大志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直想进取中原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有 还有 还有荆州刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘表也是皇亲国戚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州非你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备谨遵陶公所命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暂领徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待朝廷旨意到达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再遵旨办理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何处鸣钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}声音像是西门警钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}城守正在鸣钟报警
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹军来得好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀太守
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布率数千铁骑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正在西门即关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘将军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看吕布想攻我徐州城吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}观其阵势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不象是攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奋威将军吕布拜关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着人取来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公台先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果刘备不让我们进城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备是个仁义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在他最大的敌人是曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要抵杭曹操大军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其需要我们相助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那如果刘备收留了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就更好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}观时待变相机行事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊 吕布被曹操击败后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无处容身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在想来投靠我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这厮还有脸来投靠咱们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想当初咱哥仨揍他的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没砍他的脑袋就算他命大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}彼一时此一时嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来吕布改邢归正了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}亲手斩杀了国贼董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为汉廷立下了大功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不愧是当世英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此一节也得到了天下人的赞赏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布是员猛将
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}部下八千铁骑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果能得到他的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们就不怕曹操来犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 吕布虽勇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却素无信义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把他留在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等于养虎为患
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当心被他咬伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是就是 二哥说得是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布这厮倒是有一处好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人长得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讨女人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其它的一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这叫什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大实话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥 你想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布一共有多少个爹 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这丁原一个 董卓一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}王允一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再加上他自个儿的亲爹一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这前前后后共有四个爹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这四个爹都因吕布而死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可见他是个大灾星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁要是做了他的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可准不得好死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只想做他的友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想做他的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可这回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布不甘心做人家儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他想做人家的爹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他这回来投靠咱们这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看 就是来图谋徐州来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来刘备是不会接纳我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 再等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们都已经等了两个时辰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当初我见董卓都不需要等这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在不是当初
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备更不是董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们平心静气地想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前段日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果没有吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}偷袭曹操的根据地兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操岂能退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州岂有今日之平安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布势穷来投我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果拒而不纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成何道理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说我等如想匡扶汉室 成就大业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就必须结交各路英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眼下 我们的大敌是曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布的大敌也是曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们两家只有合军拒曹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}方能胜算在握
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操不是有句名言嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫宁肯我负天下人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}休叫天下人负我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也有句名言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宁肯天下人负我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不负天下人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公明见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开城相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥哥要见自个儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不见这厮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备他亲自出城相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记住 见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对刘备一定要十分恭敬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}败军之将吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜见徐州刺史刘玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备翘望已久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}终于把奉先和公台盼望来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日之会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令人无限欢喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快随我进城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 请
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 你可知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天底下哪家骑兵是最厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道 请将军赐教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我吕布统率的八千铁骑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你可知道那八千铁骑当中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最勇猛善战的是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是 正是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有赤兔马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可日行千里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有方天画戟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能破金断石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可知道世人是怎么称赞我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人中吕布 马中赤免
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是 正是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先 奉先 你喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们还是早点歇息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不醉不醉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}酒逢知已千杯少 来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}斟酒 斟酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 只要你我联手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自然是大业有成 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要坐守城关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每日喝酒吃茶 听歌赏月就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剩下事情呢交给我 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}率领八千铁骑 征战四方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为你打天下 等天下打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你我一人一半
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看可好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先将军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你既然如此英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何在兖州城下败于曹操呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是我败于曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是曹操败于我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}行了 不提了 不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道荥阳大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是怎么痛击曹操的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道 请将军赐教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先啊 来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们多敬敬玄德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎 那一日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夭昏地暗 日月无光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我单骑冲入敌阵当中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看见一个穿红袍的家伙正在逃命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我执戟朝他头盔上一击 大喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操何在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他回答我说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前面骑黄马的便是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我赶紧追上骑黄马那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一戟把他刺翻 一看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是一个小小的校尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来我才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才在我戟下的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然就是该死的曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一时大意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然让他在我的戟下逃生了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说曹贼他奸是不奸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奸 竟然都把奉先将军给蒙骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹阿瞒虽奸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却有雄才大略
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人言治世之能臣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乱世之奸雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奸贼与奸雄虽只差一字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却有天地悬殊哇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要有我吕布在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管他是奸贼还是奸雄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是待死鼠辈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 咱俩约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我打天下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你坐守徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你只需按月供我粮饷即可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我这个徐州刺史
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是暂时代领而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子并没有下旨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各镇诸侯也未必心服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先兄兵强马壮 英勇盖世
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又加上天子亲封奋威将军
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.34,0:23:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}授忠义侯 一统三司
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刘备却什么封号都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实在是不配提领这徐州啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:24:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道你不想要徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请奉先将军收下此印
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}领徐州刺史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先 奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘将军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们兵败相投
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.34,0:24:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能得刘将军容留已经是感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂能有非分之想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请将军万万不要生疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.95,0:24:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 强宾不压主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下只想为玄德效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.36,0:24:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}共拒曹操 保徐州太平
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.23,0:24:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先 公台
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们二位以为我在作态是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.84,0:24:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非也 我是真心愿让徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.64,0:24:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.74,0:24:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一者吕布名震天下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.65,0:24:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵强马壮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.95,0:25:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二者得公台兄相助
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.88,0:25:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何愁大业不成 三者
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.19,0:25:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操不怕我刘备却惧怕吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.69,0:25:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 只有将徐州交由你们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.76,0:25:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才可得保太平
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.56,0:25:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 玄德兄你如此说来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.33,0:25:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是在撵我们走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.53,0:25:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绝非此意 绝非此意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.94,0:25:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先啊 我们还是快快离开徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.84,0:25:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别投它处吧 以免玄德兄生疑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.54,0:25:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}且慢 这样 二位暂且歇下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.18,0:25:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事我们从长计议 可好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.39,0:25:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.36,0:25:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.23,0:25:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先哪 你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.44,0:26:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才在酒宴上你真是太轻率
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.64,0:26:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备那是作势要让徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.95,0:26:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么能去接他的关防呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.08,0:26:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是他要给 又不是我要夺他的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.49,0:26:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉呀 他那是在试探我们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.69,0:26:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备根本不是真心诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.99,0:26:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算他真心诚意要让徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.16,0:26:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他两个兄弟关羽张飞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.66,0:26:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道会答应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.36,0:26:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 行行行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.63,0:26:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那刘备的真意到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.04,0:26:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备的真意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.94,0:26:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是想施加恩典于你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.34,0:26:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将你引为已用 共拒曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.25,0:26:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.88,0:26:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也正想跟他共拒曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.08,0:26:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.89,0:26:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.19,0:26:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他的想法是以他为主
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.19,0:26:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用你为将
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.49,0:26:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的想法是以你为主
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.29,0:26:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用他为仆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.29,0:26:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你甚至想取而代之
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.06,0:26:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作徐州刺史 这能一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.44,0:27:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.74,0:27:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来刘备是真心要用我们
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.15,0:27:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也好 那我们就投其所好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.38,0:27:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁热打铁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.89,0:27:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你和他可以结拜为异姓兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.19,0:27:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把关系搞好 至于以后嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.29,0:27:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看情况再定进退
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.96,0:27:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.84,0:27:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你召我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.85,0:27:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}数月来 我劳师远征
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.19,0:27:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在兖州和徐州两地浴血苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.99,0:28:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}花费了几十万的粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.09,0:28:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却连半寸土地都没有得到
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.33,0:28:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可这个刘备 不费吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.34,0:28:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坐收徐州六郡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.74,0:28:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由此可见这个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.34,0:28:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忠厚其表 奸恶其心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.78,0:28:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下早就说过
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.08,0:28:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备表面上看像个仁义君子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.09,0:28:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但他大智若愚
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.49,0:28:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大伪似忠 厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.69,0:28:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公绝不能小视此人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.99,0:28:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我从来都没有小看过他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.50,0:28:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒是他在内心里小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.54,0:28:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公想怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.54,0:28:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我找你来 就是想跟你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.64,0:28:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想等粮草备齐之后
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.28,0:28:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就攻打刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.88,0:28:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夺回徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.18,0:28:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.39,0:29:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有何不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.39,0:29:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州乃夺取中原之要地
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.09,0:29:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们欲成大业
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.89,0:29:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必须得占领徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.69,0:29:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公三思 徐州和以前不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.97,0:29:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在刘备与吕布联手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.04,0:29:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州城是更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.74,0:29:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公率军急攻
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.44,0:29:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}势必会逼得两个人生死同心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.74,0:29:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}合力抵杭 相反
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.05,0:29:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公要是能够容忍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.68,0:29:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州城肯定是一山难容二虎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.59,0:29:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布和刘备这两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.89,0:29:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个是贪而好勇
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.59,0:29:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个是虚伪自恃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.89,0:29:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早晚会争起来 到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.90,0:29:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公再提兵取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.16,0:29:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂不是更佳
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.74,0:29:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 言之有理
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.05,0:30:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}急攻则同心相拒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.69,0:30:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宽忍则必生分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.79,0:30:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧 你想得深远 我不如你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.00,0:30:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公只是一时恼怒罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.17,0:30:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公心平气和 静下心来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.67,0:30:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}片刻就能看出这里的要害
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.84,0:30:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这话说得倒是 以后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.04,0:30:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我再恼怒过头你马上骂我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.74,0:30:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把我骂醒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.15,0:30:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下断然不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.85,0:30:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我命令你骂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.58,0:30:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.84,0:31:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}承蒙刘公厚爱
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.34,0:31:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}留我们在徐州小住
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.45,0:31:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日日宴请 百般关照
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.58,0:31:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先将军和本人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.69,0:31:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是又感动又不安哪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.59,0:31:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公台兄这话倒让我不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.19,0:31:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州就是你们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.40,0:31:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们若能长居于此
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.40,0:31:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非但刘备之幸
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.77,0:31:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是徐州全城军民之幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.57,0:31:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.37,0:31:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先将军确实感恩不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.07,0:31:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天特设家宴
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.64,0:31:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请刘公光临哪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.05,0:31:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先把家眷都带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.48,0:31:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤弟 来来来 快来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.28,0:31:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愚兄恭候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.09,0:31:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德兄慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.49,0:31:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.59,0:31:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤弟 愚兄现在是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.59,0:31:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一日不见 如隔三秋
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.50,0:31:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日我们要痛饮三百杯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.56,0:32:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.87,0:32:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是你嫂子 貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.05,0:32:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嫂夫人美名天下 刘备拜见
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.88,0:32:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贫妾不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.49,0:32:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘将军才是人中龙凤
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.69,0:32:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤弟 愚兄是略备薄酌
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.60,0:32:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为答谢你待我之厚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.66,0:32:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.47,0:32:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉 唱几出你拿手的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.67,0:32:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为刘贤弟助兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.67,0:32:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贫妾遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.57,0:32:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.48,0:32:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 贤弟请
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.39,0:33:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤弟 请
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.60,0:33:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.67,0:33:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}红牙催拍燕飞忙
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.18,0:33:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一片行云到画堂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.67,0:33:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眉黛促成游子恨
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.78,0:33:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤弟 贤弟 喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.38,0:34:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玉容初断故人肠
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.68,0:34:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟 三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.78,0:34:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了二哥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.09,0:34:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过来说话
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.89,0:34:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.19,0:34:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这吕布设什么家宴
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.19,0:34:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把咱大哥给叫去了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.10,0:34:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.36,0:34:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不就是喝个酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.77,0:34:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可知道侍宴的是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.87,0:34:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.97,0:34:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.57,0:34:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是吕布抢来的那个女的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.18,0:34:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听说此女美艳无双
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.88,0:35:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}男人碰到她呀 都会骨酥神迷
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.92,0:35:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这吕布叫她侍宴
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.72,0:35:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是给大哥摆得什么阵
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.99,0:35:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥戎马半生 心肠又软 这不
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.09,0:35:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好哇吕布这厮
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.09,0:35:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用自家娘们勾引咱哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.89,0:35:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这还得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.70,0:35:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们得想个办法 把大哥弄回来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.56,0:35:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别中了吕布的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.47,0:35:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.57,0:35:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一枪挑了她就是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.37,0:35:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟 三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.77,0:35:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可鲁莽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.22,0:35:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军请
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.62,0:35:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢嫂夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.89,0:35:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德 今天起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.19,0:35:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们就是自家兄弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.99,0:35:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生死同舟 荣辱与共
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.20,0:35:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来 喝酒 喝酒 来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.26,0:35:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.47,0:35:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布 我哥哥是金枝玉叶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.87,0:36:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这厮竟敢叫他做贤弟
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.17,0:36:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是什么东西 三姓家奴
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.98,0:36:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大灾星 这丁原 董卓 王允
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.48,0:36:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是被你这个家奴害死的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.81,0:36:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你现在又觍着脸
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.12,0:36:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要来巴结我哥不成
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.62,0:36:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}羞死人了 呸
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.02,0:36:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟 快快住口
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.99,0:36:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布你听着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.39,0:36:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你张爷爷把你那小戟儿带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.59,0:36:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赶快拿上你的兵器过来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.29,0:36:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过来跟张爷爷大战三百回合
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.30,0:36:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.17,0:36:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布 你听着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.37,0:36:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爷爷在关前等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.37,0:36:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.68,0:36:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先兄 嫂夫人 真是对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.58,0:36:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我三弟是个粗人 不知礼法
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.02,0:36:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我替他向你们陪罪 得罪得罪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.72,0:36:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军其实不必在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.19,0:36:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们都知道 这刘关张三兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.99,0:36:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是天下的大英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.80,0:36:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德 你别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.87,0:37:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我吕布再傻也明白事理
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.27,0:37:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州我是不能留了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.57,0:37:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我今天就走
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.97,0:37:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先兄想哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.97,0:37:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大丈夫四海为家
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.08,0:37:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我凭方天画戟赤兔马
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.88,0:37:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何愁没容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.52,0:37:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先兄 可否这样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.72,0:37:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州城外五十里处有边城小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.69,0:37:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那也是我先前驻兵之处
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.20,0:37:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先可率军暂时驻扎小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.87,0:37:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 粮草军饷
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.47,0:37:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}俱有徐州供给 可否
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.87,0:37:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看可以啊 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.48,0:37:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小沛与徐州城成犄角之势
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.78,0:37:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一旦有警
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.98,0:37:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们两军可以互相应援
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.52,0:37:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先哪 快 谢过玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.70,0:38:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然如此 拜谢玄德了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.07,0:38:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.57,0:38:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下这就领命前往小沛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.22,0:38:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.32,0:38:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我吕布竟然落到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.63,0:38:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}替人看门守关
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.13,0:38:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当年韩信有胯下之辱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.86,0:38:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张良有拾履之羞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.57,0:38:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军和他们相比
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.47,0:38:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}羞与辱还差得远
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.47,0:38:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}威与福倒是多得多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.87,0:38:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们下一步该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.78,0:38:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暂居小沛 招兵买马
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.81,0:38:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}观时待变
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.32,0:39:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好好 这灾星走了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.53,0:39:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们少了个大麻烦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.43,0:39:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}麻烦事在后面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.90,0:39:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操战败吕布已有半月
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.57,0:39:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}按理早就该向徐州用兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.57,0:39:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是到现在兖州方向
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.97,0:39:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直没有任何动作
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.87,0:39:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知在谋划什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.58,0:39:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怕什么 徐州城是座坚城
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.88,0:39:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粮饷充足 曹操敢来犯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.02,0:39:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我必迎头痛击
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.62,0:39:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是就是 多日不打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.42,0:39:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这手都痒痒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.32,0:39:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这整天除了喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.52,0:39:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也没别的事情做 难过得紧哪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.53,0:39:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这曹操要是再不来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.10,0:39:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干脆我们打到兖州去找他算了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.68,0:39:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.28,0:39:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.48,0:40:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}董承从长安派来一密使
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.71,0:40:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秘密传达天子诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.22,0:40:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.52,0:40:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那使臣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.92,0:40:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饿得只剩下一把骨头了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.32,0:40:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚刚进门就昏了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.03,0:40:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我派人把他送到后院喝粥去了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.40,0:40:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.37,0:40:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀大夫 究竟发生什么事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.87,0:41:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让末将也知道一点嘛
